    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A crystalline phenol, obtained naturally from various types of resin or artificially; used especially in making dye, pharmaceuticals, and resin.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
